{"id":"Mo3Ju9MKZYXP29iJoFhJ","slug":"authentic-pho","seoDesc":"Authentic Pho Recipe (Vietnamese Noodle Soup), Pho is a soup consisting of bone broth, rice noodles, thinly-sliced meat","imgCoverWebP":"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/authentic-aftertaste.appspot.com/o/recipe%2Fauthentic-pho%2Fauthentic-pho.png?alt=media&token=a0f1ca35-590b-4203-9340-fc5947664325","authorLink":"","cuisine":"Vietnamese","information":"<p>Pho is a soup consisting of bone broth, rice noodles, thinly-sliced meat (in this recipe, it's beef), and fresh garnishes.</p>","description":"Pho is a soup consisting of bone broth, rice noodles, thinly-sliced meat (in this recipe, it's beef), and fresh garnishes.","imgThumb":"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/authentic-aftertaste.appspot.com/o/recipe%2Fauthentic-pho%2Fauthentic-pho-thumb.png?alt=media&token=69fcf37e-2688-42e0-ad6c-3d6d7ab35298","serving":"6","nutritions":[{"value":"885","name":"calories","order":"1"},{"order":"2","value":"102.2 g","name":"carbohydrates"},{"value":"174.4 mg","name":"cholesterol","order":"3"},{"value":"1745.4 mg","name":"sodium","order":"4"},{"name":"fat","order":"5","value":"23.9 g"},{"name":"protein","value":"60.5 g","order":"6"}],"keywords":"authentic pho, vietnamese noodle soup","time":{"prep":"1 hr","additional":"","cook":"8 hrs","total":"9 hrs"},"ratings":{"avg":"4.75","count":4},"directions":[{"desc":"Place the beef bones in a 9-quart (or larger) pot. Season with salt, and fill pot with 2 gallons of water. Bring to a boil, reduce heat, and simmer for about 2 hours.","imgWebP":"","img":"","order":"1"},{"order":"2","desc":"Meanwhile, preheat broiler. Put onions and unpeeled ginger on a foil-lined, 10x15-inch roasting pan. Broil 4 to 5 inches from heat until onion and ginger are charred, 10 to 15 minutes. Cool slightly. Chop onions. Peel and slice ginger.","img":"","imgWebP":""},{"imgWebP":"","img":"","desc":"Skim fat from surface of broth, and add oxtail, daikon, and charred onions. Tie anise, cinnamon stick, cloves, peppercorns and charred ginger in a square of cheesecloth; add to broth. Stir in sugar, fish sauce, and remaining 2 tsp. salt. Simmer over medium-low heat at least 4 hours (the longer, the better). Strain broth. Discard spices and bones. Reserve meat from bones for other uses, if desired. Taste broth and add additional salt as needed. Chill overnight.","order":"3"},{"order":"4","desc":"Skim fat from top of chilled broth. Bring broth to a boil; reduce heat and keep hot until ready to serve.","img":"","imgWebP":""},{"imgWebP":"","img":"","desc":"Cook rice noodles in boiling water according to package directions until soft, but not mushy. Cut sirloin into paper-thin slices. ","order":"5"},{"desc":"Divide noodles among bowls (1 1/2 cups per bowl). Top each with a few raw sirloin slices. Ladle boiling broth into bowls to cook beef and cover noodles.","img":"","imgWebP":"","order":"6"}],"name":"Authentic Pho","modified":"2022-05-26","seoTitle":"How To Make Authentic Pho - Vietnamese Noodle Soup Recipe","author":"Jennifer Miller","imgThumbWebP":"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/authentic-aftertaste.appspot.com/o/recipe%2Fauthentic-pho%2Fauthentic-pho-thumb.webp?alt=media&token=7f69e9eb-a1cf-421a-bfa4-6b129fa145ed","ingredients":[{"order":"1","quantity":"4","ingredient":"beef soup bones","quantityExtra":"","unit":"pounds","note":"shank and knee"},{"order":"2","unit":"","quantityExtra":"","ingredient":"medium onion","quantity":"1","note":"unpeeled and cut in half"},{"unit":"","quantityExtra":"","quantity":"5","note":"","ingredient":"slices fresh ginger","order":"3"},{"ingredient":"salt","quantityExtra":"","order":"4","unit":"tablespoon","quantity":"1","note":""},{"quantity":"2","note":"","order":"5","ingredient":"star anise","unit":"pods","quantityExtra":""},{"note":"","order":"6","quantityExtra":"1/2","ingredient":"fish sauce","unit":"tablespoons","quantity":"2"},{"unit":"quarts","ingredient":"water","quantityExtra":"","order":"7","quanti